                Aim of the T&I: 
            </h3>
            <p class="text">
                 As with most software projects, the main motivation of this project is to make people's lives easier. More specifically,
                  the project mainly focuses on translation. Although it is very easy to communicate with technology over the internet, 
                  the aim of our project is to make face-to-face communication between different languages ​​much easier. The project should 
                  provide unicast, multicast and broadcast communication types for multilingual conferences. The main purpose of this project 
                  is to provide users with instant translation.
            </p>
