                <h3 class="title">
                    The Offered Value
                </h3>
                <p class="text">Today, the translation of the spoken language into the desired language is provided by human translators 
                    at conferences and meetings. This enables communication but also wastes money and time. Our goal is to develop a system
                     that saves time and money and provides a more effective way of communication. However, in our research on this sector,
                      we realized that most of them do not support Turkish. This situation obliges Turkish users to know a language other than 
                      their mother tongue. Our main goal is to solve these problems in our project.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="width: 440px; margin-left: 210px;">
